Offering Profile

Overview/Objectives 
Strategy 
Risk Factors 




Strategy
NYC REIT has focused and intends to continue focusing our investment activities on acquiring quality, income-producing commercial real estate located in the five boroughs of New York City and, in particular, properties located in Manhattan. We may also originate or acquire real estate debt backed by quality, income-producing commercial real estate located predominantly in New York City. The real estate debt, which we may also originate or acquire is expected to be primarily first mortgage debt but also may include bridge loans, mezzanine loans, preferred equity or securitized loans
The three primary objectives are*:

Preserve and protect capital
Pay monthly stable cash distributions; and
Increase the value of assets in order to generate capital appreciation.



     *There is no guarantee these objectives will be met.
     






















