NYC REIT Buying Office Tower From Blackstone For $180M



        By Andrew McIntyre



					Law360, Minneapolis (March 23, 2016, 11:53 AM EDT) -- American Realty Capital New York City REIT Inc. is under contract to purchase a New York office property from a Blackstone Group LP affiliate for $180 million, according to an announcement from the real estate investment trust on Wednesday.The deal is for the 22-story Midtown 1140 Avenue of the Americas, a 250,000-square-foot tower. The seller is a Blackstone Real Estate Partners VI LP affiliate.“We are pleased to announce the acquisition of 1140 Avenue of the Americas, which enjoys a prime central midtown Manhattan location with...
				
